name: Nemona / ネモ (Pokemon)
description:
Nemona from Pokemon trained on 52 SFW and NSFW images.

Use nemona \(pokemon\) to generate Nemona. For her full outfit, use:

  • white collared shirt

  • orange necktie

  • orange shorts

  • black pantyhose

  • sneakers

Other modifiers include:

  • bag

  • pokeball

  • black glove

For more consistent results when generating, you can use extra descriptor tags such as freckles, ponytail, stripped shorts, etc. Since her hair is fairly unique, sometimes the AI may have a trouble generating the right number of strands, but it can easily be fixed with some quick inpainting. twintails in the negative prompt can help too. Her glove is also hit or miss due to the uniqueness of its design.
